{
  "stem": "22803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- where the-- the other people saluted with their hands stretched out, he always saluted like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he greeted my mother and me, because we just had the misfortune to cross the street as he came out of his house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we, of course, just walked by and ignored it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later on, of course, there was a little more-- what-- I mean, he always had the limousine waiting outside the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it used to wait there for hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in the early years, he would just walk out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When the children-- when he came out, he came out with his little dog.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had a little-- well, we called it a fox terrier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think here you call them wire-hair terrier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he always had a whip in his hand, like just, you know, like a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not really that he was whipping anybody at that time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But-- and he would go to the limousine with his little dog.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the children came across and he would hand out oranges to the children, because oranges-- Germany had no foreign exchange, so oranges that came from Italy or Africa were a rare commodity.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the children used to walk-- run across and he would hand out oranges.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I used to go and run across too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I didn't take any oranges.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I just--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I knew I was a Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hang-- you know, I held to the back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- but, you know, just ran with the rest of the group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the story, I'm-- even why I'm telling this, because the proximity to Hitler is what, I think, I undid my parents in the end.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
